              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-1" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hze">Cyprus • Yacht</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-3" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:xmoest">Luxury Yacht Celebration</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hzd">An intimate and high-end experience aboard a private luxury yacht, featuring sunset cruising and premium dining.</p>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:fjets7">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:5z62cp">Charter From</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-6" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:fjets6">
              <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:5z62co">£3,850</span>
