            <img crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534447677768-be436bb09401?auto=format&w=800&q=80" alt="Traditional Greek Schooner" class="w-full h-full object-cover" loading="lazy" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:i1ny5b" />
