            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hzb">A charming and authentic sailing experience on a traditional wooden boat, perfect for rustic sea-themed weddings.</p>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:fjetrd">
