                  </div>
                </div>
                <span class="text-secondary font-bold text-[10px]" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:5z626p">4.8</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground mb-1" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hza">Ibiza • Catamaran</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold font-serif text-secondary mb-3" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:xmoesr">Party Catamaran</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground mb-4" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hz9">Celebrate in style with a spacious catamaran wedding, offering plenty of room for dancing and panoramic island views.</p>
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-2 mb-2" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:fjetqj">
              <span class="text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted-foreground" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:5z62bu">Charter From</span>
            </div>
