      <h2 class="text-[36px] font-bold font-serif text-secondary text-center mb-12" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:iy9hkf">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-muted-foreground text-center mb-10" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hz8">Everything you need to know about planning a wedding at sea</p>

      <div class="space-y-4 max-w-3xl mx-auto" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:fjetqf">
        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:xmoesq">Can we have the legal ceremony on the boat?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hz7">Legal ceremonies on boats depend on the local maritime laws of the destination. Often, the legal paperwork is completed at a nearby town hall, followed by a beautiful symbolic ceremony on board.</p>
        </details>

        <details class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="flex justify-between items-center cursor-pointer list-none">
            <h3 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-secondary" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:xmoes4">What happens if the weather is bad for our boat wedding?</h3>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-primary transition-transform group-open:rotate-180" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <p class="text-muted-foreground mt-4 leading-relaxed" data-ps="src/components/wedding-type/BoatWeddingsContent.astro:z90hyl">We always have contingency plans. Most boats have covered areas, or we can arrange a nearby shore-based venue as a backup to ensure your day goes ahead perfectly.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

